[size=15pt][b]About[/b][/size] Sayyox Ltd is a Runescape server development group that is the founders and operators of Smash on Sight. Founded by ‘Ixl Adds Ixl’ who is the lead GFX and developer for Sayyox ltd and Smash on Sight. Contacts should be emailed to contact@sayyox.com - your query will be answered within 48 hours of response.
[b][size=15pt]History[/size][/b] Sayyox Ltd was first introduced to Runescape server development in January 2008. At first the group was known as “iExcel Studio” but got exchanged for another name since it was already taken which was later discovered during the expiring time of February. So the name then became “Sayyox Ltd”.
